What We Do — Philo Media








































 Philo Media













Philo works with advertisers to create and distribute branded video content. 




Concept Development



Production



Distribution




Concept Development— The Industry’s Best Thinkers Our team of talented creatives have developed countless digital programs amassing millions of views. They are constantly pushing boundaries in order to stay ahead of the curve and would love to talk about the future of your video content.







Production— Award-winning Production Quality video is quality video regardless of where it’s viewed. Whether on the big screen or mobile device, Philo delivers the highest production value and we work with you to make the execution simple. 









Distribution— The Right Audience				You've invested a lot of time, effort and money into creating compelling video content and you deserve to know its being viewed the right way. Philo delivers your highly targeted custom programming on proven, trusted first-party platforms across mobile devices and connected screens.			






						Guaranteed Views					




						YouTube TrueView					




						Facebook Video					












About Us — Philo Media










































 Philo Media












Philo’s mission is to create and distribute the world’s most compelling branded video.

↓ Take a peek into our culture ↓


Culture Principle #1
Respect


For ourselves, our partners and our work. We believe in fostering an environment free of judgment. We appreciate one another. Philo is a place where you can freely and safely express yourself and your ideas.









Culture Principle #2
Passion


We like smart people that aren’t afraid of accountability and like pushing themselves and their peers outside of their comfort zone. We are a group of individuals that care deeply about our individual and collective contributions, the end result and success of our partners.









Culture Principle #3
Betterment


Always striving to better yourself and others around you. Philo is a place where you can learn and develop as an employee and individual. We encourage a balanced and positive lifestyle.









Culture Principle #4
Adventure


We like to take informed risks and explore new ideas. It fuels our creative desires, maintains a challenging environment, and keeps us ahead of the curve.






Culture Principle #5
Communication


Full transparency, honesty and openness internally within Philo and externally with the world.

















Want to learn more about Philo?  Connect with us on Social
